{"tid":990381,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"清水健獲封爵","createTime":"2019-01-21T14:00:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-22T11:11:22.000Z","uid":184679,"like":485,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"3e68881a0d51ecbb6942867bc0406f99ce14c9a7","tid":990381,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T14:00:38.000Z","msg":"AV界天王清水健因工作奉旨要同無數女性肉搏，更曾被爆有至少103個性伴侶，噚日佢就透露獲封爵，由AV男優升格做AV男爵，成為日本首位AV男爵。<br />\n<br />\n其實清水健並非因為喺AV界嘅偉績獲封爵，只係佢於2017年12月曾經去到位於英國南東部嘅西蘭公國（Principality of Sealand），用14,000日圓買（約1,000港元）下爵位，隔咗成年終於收到承認佢封爵嘅證書，清水健收到證書後都表現得好興奮。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190121/59167977\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190121%2F59167977&d=1L79tNmClEUrvu3H0gBFjP1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=29acad3c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190121%2F59167977&h=f530bcf3\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190121/59167977</a>"},{"pid":"3f5b7808dedf29648fee9bc8e247f34cc798dfa5","tid":990381,"uid":94828,"like":162,"dislike":1,"score":161,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T14:03:23.000Z","msg":"西蘭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfdc0849db52224633c8ff8aaf2b73a0677bf248","tid":990381,"uid":13468,"like":283,"dislike":2,"score":281,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T14:05:08.000Z","msg":"令我諗起劉爵士<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-RgQg8Ikfchk/Tkk2QQroeqI/AAAAAAAAAFE/d9cLLc7US-w/s640/01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-RgQg8Ikfchk%2FTkk2QQroeqI%2FAAAAAAAAAFE%2Fd9cLLc7US-w%2Fs640%2F01.jpg&h=aa980514&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eda39e5d297018b93665a41292c55703c3163f3e","tid":990381,"uid":56698,"like":86